  "description": "A stunning long-exposure photograph captures a vast, rocky desert landscape under a brilliant night sky. The ground is covered in dark, small stones and sparse vegetation.  In the distance, silhouetted mountains rise against the deepening blue of the twilight or early evening sky. Above, the Milky Way stretches across the frame, appearing as a dense band of countless stars. Several bright stars and planets are visible as distinct points of light, adding to the celestial spectacle. The lighting is dramatic, with a clear contrast between the dark foreground and the luminous sky.",
